  "time_ut": 1656429371,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dbd \u0d86\u0daf\u0dcf\u0dba\u0db8\u0dca \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Concession period for revenue licenses of Western vehicles",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Chief Secretariats of the Western Province have decided to grant a grace period for obtaining revenue licenses for vehicles registered in the Western Province in view of the crisis situation prevailing in the country.",
        "Accordingly, no fines will be levied on the issuance of revenue licenses for vehicles registered in the Western Province until the 29th of July. Further states."
      ],
